<title>&quot;SEND THE LIGHT&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuilien kinawk gal apat sapna a hung,
 &quot;Salh vakin........, salh vakin!&quot;
 Thagau mangthai hukdam ding tampi a um,
 &quot;Salh vakin........, salh vakin!&quot;

[V2]
 Salh vakin ....., Gospel vak deihum chuh,
 Leisiet kawl ....kim salh vek hen!
 Salh vakin ....., Gospel vak deihum chuh,
 Kumkhuo'n salh....vak suok zing hen!

[V3]
 2. Makedonia mite sapna I zau ui,
 &quot;Salh vakin......, salh vakin!&quot;
 I thilpiek kipahum Kross bulah I ngau,
 &quot;Salh vakin......, salh vakin!&quot;

[V4]
 3. Isu lungsietna mitin kawmah tung hen,
 &quot;Salh vakin....., salh vakin!&quot;
 Muntin ah Krista lunggil bang mi'n puu hen,
 &quot;Salh vakin....., salh vakin!&quot;

[V5]
 4. Hehpihna nasepna chuh chimchak puoi tiu,
 &quot;Salh vakin ....., salh vakin!&quot;
 Lukhuk zem ding suongmantam I khawl lai hin,
 &quot;Salh vakin......, salh vakin!&quot;</lyrics>
</song>